  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>PHYSICS BASED</u></i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destructible Structures  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab / manipulate objects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Active Ragdolls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physical bullets, no hit-scan  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Projectile deflection</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440580/extras/16d7d5ea8f1b13015e2ac6f1dab23fd4.poster.avif?t=1773776750\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440580/extras/16d7d5ea8f1b13015e2ac6f1dab23fd4.webm?t=1773776750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440580/extras/16d7d5ea8f1b13015e2ac6f1dab23fd4.mp4?t=1773776750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i><strong>MOVEMENT</strong></i></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kick Boost</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slide</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dash</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Momentum</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440580/extras/9ea66f2211339fc10676a364245ad6fd.poster.avif?t=1773776750\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440580/extras/9ea66f2211339fc10676a364245ad6fd.webm?t=1773776750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440580/extras/9ea66f2211339fc10676a364245ad6fd.mp4?t=1773776750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>UNIQUE WEAPONS & GEAR</u></i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40+ weapons to wield</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15+ equipment variants</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20+ enemy types to destroy</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Vehicles to crash</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weaponize your food by regurgitating </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440580/extras/59f8520bdbd439120cc8cb2fbba7f3dc.poster.avif?t=1773776750\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440580/extras/59f8520bdbd439120cc8cb2fbba7f3dc.webm?t=1773776750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440580/extras/59f8520bdbd439120cc8cb2fbba7f3dc.mp4?t=1773776750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><u>PSEUDO RPG PROGRESSION</u></i></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up mastery through weapon use</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find coins to purchase stat upgrades</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase your gluttony level by gorging yourself</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep mastery progression on death,  no attempt is in vain </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
